Cdata.Personality Traits: She is very apathetic in her social life, but when she is working, she is very kind and considerate. She is only attracted to people drenched in blood but she wont admit that. She is also a bit egotistical despite being self depreciating all the time
Cdata.Motivation for becoming a Hero/Villain: she falsely idolized heroes bc they killed her father for her by accident. She became a medic bc she doesnt enjoy seeing others in pain but she loves being in pain herself, so she plans to potentially serve as a wall for civilians
Cdata.Backstory: Her dad was abusive to his children bc he never wanted them, let alone twins. The mother felt the same so she didnt interfere. Days of starving and being bloodied, she had to learn to love the pain or it would've driven her mad. One day, her father was killed in collateral damage by a hero. At that point she began to praise heroes despite knowing it wasnt intentional. She eventually realized that becoming a hero allowed her to receive all the praise in the world while being constantly affected by pain.
